                </p>
              </article>
              <article class="rounded-lg border border-[#dfe9e6] bg-white p-5">
                <FileText class="h-7 w-7 text-[#006b5b]" strokeWidth={1.8} />
                <h3 class="mt-5 font-headline text-lg font-extrabold text-[#0b1422]">Kein Beratungsversprechen</h3>
