            </p>
            <a class="mt-5 inline-flex items-center rounded-md font-label text-sm font-bold text-[#006b5b] transition hover:text-[#005346] focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-[#006b5b]/35 focus-visible:ring-offset-4" href="/kontakt">
